{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 271149, "create_time": 1656780542, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "诺兰的信条，星际穿越都不错吧", "timestamp": 1656780542}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 271197, "create_time": 1656783684, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "所有艺术形式在前中期都是容易突破的，到后期就会难以持续创新.. 不仅电影艺术，流行乐、小说、话剧的好作品都在枯竭.", "timestamp": 1656783684}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 271203, "create_time": 1656783984, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "而且你列举的片在艺术性上也并没有什么突破.", "timestamp": 1656783984}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 271209, "create_time": 1656784307, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "横向比较的话，华语作品还真称不上枯竭. 新世纪以来，华语导演可是拍出了不少现象级作品. ", "timestamp": 1656784307}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 271216, "create_time": 1656784618, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "《花样年华》《一一》《三峡好人》《刺客聂隐娘》这些亚洲电影的扛鼎之作都是21世纪的电影.", "timestamp": 1656784618}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 271244, "create_time": 1656786714, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "“业界要凉”永不过时", "timestamp": 1656786714}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 271405, "create_time": 1656813222, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Alice: 信条就算了，真不咋地", "timestamp": 1656813222}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 271409, "create_time": 1656813298, "is_blocked": false, "is_tm